org.slf4j.helpers
Class NOPLogger

java.lang.Object
  org.slf4j.helpers.NOPLogger
All Implemented Interfaces:
Logger
public class NOPLogger
extends Object
implements Logger

A direct NOP (no operation) implementation of Logger.

This is a reduced version to support CLDC 1.1

Author:
Ceki Gülcü, Marcel Patzlaff
